import React, { Component } from 'react';

class Form extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <form>
        <label htmlFor="nomeCarta">Nome Carta</label>
        <input
          id="nomeCarta"
          name="name"
          type="text"
          data-testid="name-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="descricaoCarta">Descrição</label>
        <input
          id="descricaoCarta"
          name="description"
          type="textarea"
          data-testid="name-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="atributo01">Attr01</label>
        <input
          id="atributo01"
          name="attr01"
          type="number"
          data-testid="attr1-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="atributo02">Attr02</label>
        <input
          id="atributo02"
          name="attr02"
          type="number"
          data-testid="attr2-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="atributo03">Attr03</label>
        <input
          id="atributo03"
          name="attr03"
          type="number"
          data-testid="attr3-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="imagemCarta">Imagem</label>
        <input
          id="imagemCarta"
          name="imageCard"
          type="text"
          data-testid="image-input"
        />
        <label htmlFor="rareCard">Raridade</label>
        <select id="rareCard" name="rareCardSelect" data-testid="rare-input">
          <option>normal</option>
          <option>raro</option>
          <option>muito raro</option>
        </select>

        <label htmlFor="temTrunfo">Super Tryunfo Da Trybe</label>
        <input
          id="temTrunfo"
          name="checkBoxTryunfo"
          type="checkbox"
          data-testid="trunfo-input"
        />

        <button data-testid="save-button">
          Salvar
        </button>

      </form>
    );
  }
}

export default Form;
